data.description: Don't miss out on this fantastic opportunity to move into the highly sought after Deer Park neighborhood of Park Hill Estates! This huge ranch home backs to a beautiful pond on 1.75 acres with a 3 car garage. The finished walkout basement offers multi generational living with a second kitchen, wet bar, bedroom and bath with tons of additional storage space.  Bring your decorating ideas and endless possibilities await!
